newsitem.title: MEXICO: Mexico's TIIE 28-day rate rises to 32.1650 pct.
newsitem.headline: Mexico's TIIE 28-day rate rises to 32.1650 pct.

text.p: Mexico's 28-day interbank interest rate rose by 42.50 basis points to 32.1650 percent on Tuesday, from 31.7500 percent on Monday, Banco de Mexico said.
The TIIE is a market-weighted average interbank rate that is revised daily.
